Figured it out. I had to surround the space with single quotation marks as shown below:

    @CsvSource({
                    &quot;&#39; &#39;,lastName&quot;
    })

you can try one of this solutions:

 1. You can escape space value using double quotes, like this: 
```
@ParameterizedTest
@CsvSource({
    &quot;\&quot; \&quot;,lastName&quot;
})
void test(String firstName, String lastName) {
    // Your test logic
}

```

 2. You can use an escape sequence for a space, such as `\s`. This should ensure that a space character is passed as the value for firstName, like this:

```
@ParameterizedTest
@CsvSource({
    &quot;\\s,lastName&quot;
})
void test(String firstName, String lastName) {
     // Your test logic
}

```

